                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240715-108-off576 t18240715-108-cd577"></join>, four yards of floor cloth, value, 19 s.
            </rs>; the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240715-108-victim988" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Pitt
